ScaleTracks has received highly positive reviews in:

***BBC Music Magazine***
***Music Teacher Magazine***
***Piano Professional Magazine***
***The Strad***

This app has received endorsements by leading music educators and even a top Hollywood Film Composer!

TURN BORING SCALE PRACTICE IN TO AN EXCITING MUSICAL EXPERIENCE WITH SCALETRACKS. 
———————————————————

Gone are the dreaded days and endless hours of slaving away practising dry, dull exercises without musicality. With this revolutionary app, you can now play along to accompaniments that turn your scales & arpeggios into an exciting musical experience.

This app features a vast library of incredible backing tracks that accompany you as if you are playing in a live ensemble such as a jazz ensemble, brass band or even a full symphony orchestra! You can even change the tempo in real time to assist with progress!

KEY FEATURES

•ScaleTracks is remarkably easy to use, displaying a scrolling score of the chosen scale or arpeggio while you play;
•ScaleTracks features REAL musicians, not basic MIDI sounds;
•ScaleTracks contains a vast library of over 120 unique, catchy, professionally-composed backing tracks that cover every major and minor key;
•ScaleTracks is compatible with most melodic instruments (transposing instruments will be catered for in a future update); 
•ScaleTracks is suitable for all ages and ability levels;
•ScaleTracks covers a wide variety of genres from Baroque to Dubstep; 
•ScaleTracks can be set to play at any tempo that suits you;
•ScaleTracks offers you a better understanding of harmony by giving true harmonisations of scales and arpeggios with each track, which in turn opens the door to improvisation and composition;
•Play along with a brass band, rock group or symphony orchestra, and many more ensembles, from the comfort of your living room or practice studio;
•ScaleTracks is a great way to prepare for any music exam.

The amazing accompaniments complement every single note you play in a huge variety of styles.  ScaleTracks can help you improve and enhance:

• Intonation
• Rhythm
• Harmonic awareness
• Aural skills
• your technique

For the most immersive experience, we recommend pairing your phone to a Bluetooth speaker. 

** The in-app purchase 'Activate all tracks' is only required for legacy versions prior to version 1.3. **


Interested in improvisation? Check out out other app ScaleTracks JAM, which features real musicians performing epic jam tracks that are instantly transposable.  Full guitar tab is included for every scale.  Improvise using your own instrument or the in-build SUPERSOUND Deluxe keyboard.
